  <brief_title>Rehabilitation in Chronic Obstructive Pulmonary Disease (COPD) Patients With Emphysema</brief_title>
  <official_title>Effectiveness of Pulmonary Rehabilitation in Chronic Obstructive Pulmonary Disease (COPD) Patients With Emphysema Phenotype</official_title>
